{"segment":4,"line_start":301,"line_end":400,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_gun_zi","speaker_name":"棍子","listener":null,"text":"金子是你的？","tone":"陈述","chapter":6,"line_start":312,"line_end":312},{"speaker":"char_guo_da_lu","speaker_name":"郭大路","listener":null,"text":"是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":6,"line_start":314,"line_end":314},{"speaker":"char_gun_zi","speaker_name":"棍子","listener":null,"text":"从哪里来的？","tone":"陈述","chapter":6,"line_start":316,"line_end":316},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":null,"text":"呼","tone":"陈述","chapter":6,"line_start":330,"line_end":330},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":null,"text":"不变就是变，以不变应万变。","tone":"陈述","chapter":6,"line_start":352,"line_end":352},{"speaker":"char_guo_da_lu","speaker_name":"郭大路","listener":null,"text":"乘胜追击","tone":"陈述","chapter":6,"line_start":362,"line_end":362},{"speaker":"char_guo_da_lu","speaker_name":"郭大路","listener":null,"text":"是他的火气大，是他想来揍我，我哪有甚么火气？","tone":"陈述","chapter":6,"line_start":370,"line_end":370},{"speaker":"char_jin_mao_shi","speaker_name":"金毛狮","listener":null,"text":"误会误会，大家全是误会。","tone":"陈述","chapter":6,"line_start":372,"line_end":372},{"speaker":"char_guo_da_lu","speaker_name":"郭大路","listener":null,"text":"但他问了我半天，我倒也想问他一句话。","tone":"疑问","chapter":6,"line_start":374,"line_end":374},{"speaker":"char_jin_mao_shi","speaker_name":"金毛狮","listener":null,"text":"请问。","tone":"疑问","chapter":6,"line_start":376,"line_end":376},{"speaker":"char_guo_da_lu","speaker_name":"郭大路","listener":null,"text":"一个人用金子来买酒买肉，是不是犯法？","tone":"陈述","chapter":6,"line_start":378,"line_end":378},{"speaker":"char_jin_mao_shi","speaker_name":"金毛狮","listener":null,"text":"当然不犯法，我也常常用金子来付账的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":6,"line_start":380,"line_end":380},{"speaker":"char_guo_da_lu","speaker_name":"郭大路","listener":null,"text":"既然不犯法，就请你们放过麦老广，也放过我吧。","tone":"陈述","chapter":6,"line_start":382,"line_end":382},{"speaker":"char_jin_mao_shi","speaker_name":"金毛狮","listener":null,"text":"当然当然。","tone":"陈述","chapter":6,"li